refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
boolxml_set_external_entity_ref_handler XMLParserparser callablehandler
Sets the external entity reference handler function for the XML parser parser.

&reftitle.changelog;





    &Version;
    &Description;



    &xml.changelog.parser-param;


    7.3.0

     The return value of the handler is no longer
     ignored if the extension has been built against libxml. Formerly, the return
     value has been ignored, and parsing did never stop.
